quote.summary: SenseTime Group Inc is a company principally engaged in the research, development and application of artificial intelligence (AI) infrastructure and big models. With the synergy of AI infrastructure SenseCore and large model set SenseNova, the Company's business covers three sectors: generative AI, traditional AI and smart auto. The generative AI business mainly provides customers with services such as large model training, fine-tuning and inferencing with generative AI technology and infrastructure resources. The traditional AI business mainly provides customers with related products and services with non-generative AI technologies such as computer vision. The smart auto business mainly provides automakers with products and services such as autonomous driving and smart cabin. The Company's products are mainly used in the fields of Internet, smart hardware, robotics, medical care and finance.
